J. K. DAVIDSON et al. v. BOARD OF COUNTY COMMISSIONERS OF the COUNTY OF WYANDOTTE, State of KANSAS. No. 539. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. March 1, 1932. Harding, Murphy & Tucker, of Kansas City, Mo., for appellants. Roland Boynton, Atty. Gen., for, appel-lee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PEE CUEIAM.

Appeal dismissed on stipulation.
